---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 03 - 난이도 [수능] 도전</title>
		<!-- KaTeX -->
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body {
				background-color: #e0e0e0;
				margin: 0;
				padding: 20px;
				display: flex;
				justify-content: center;
			}
			.sol-button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 4px 12px;
				background: #fff8e1;
				color: #a0522d;
				border-radius: 8px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				font-weight: bold;
				margin-left: 10px;
				border: 1.5px solid #a0522d;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
			}
			.sol-button:hover {
				background: #a0522d;
				color: white;
				transform: translateY(-1px);
				box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(160, 82, 45, 0.2);
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 03. 미정계수의 결정 [수능]" chapter="Level: CSAT">
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🔴 심화 포인트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>다항함수의 추론과 미정계수</li>
					<li>무한대 극한과 특정 상수 극한의 결합</li>
					<li>인수정리를 활용한 식 세우기</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">수능 및 모의고사 '쉬운 4점' 수준의 대표 문항들입니다. 조건들을 조합하여 다항식을 완성해 보세요.</p>
					
					<!-- Q1 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><span class="pencil-star">★</span> <b>Q1.</b> 다항함수 { "$ f(x) $" }가 다음 두 조건을 만족시킬 때, { "$ f(2) $" }의 값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type03-high/q1" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box">
							(가) { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{f(x)}{3x^2 + x - 1} = 1 $" }<br/>
							(나) { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 1} \\frac{f(x)}{x-1} = 4 $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q2 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><span class="pencil-star">★</span> <b>Q2.</b> 다항함수 { "$ f(x) $" }에 대하여 다음이 성립할 때, { "$ f(3) $" }의 값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type03-high/q2" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box">
							(가) { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{f(x)-x^{3}}{x^{2}} = -2 $" }<br/>
							(나) { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{f(x)}{x} = 5 $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q3 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><span class="pencil-star">★</span> <b>Q3.</b> 삼차함수 { "$ f(x) $" }가 다음 조건을 만족한다. { "$ f(4) $" }의 값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type03-high/q3" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box">
							(가) { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 1} \\frac{f(x)}{x-1} = 6 $" }<br/>
							(나) { "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 2} \\frac{f(x)}{x-2} = 9 $" }
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-top: 40px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;">
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type03/" class="problem-link" style="margin: 0;">← 핵심 문제로 이동</a>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-inf/" class="problem-link" style="margin: 0; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.05); color: #666;">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
